com.complexible.common.netty.codec.http
Class ByteBufHttpInputStream

java.lang.Object
  java.io.InputStream
      com.complexible.common.netty.codec.http.ByteBufHttpInputStream
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable
public final class ByteBufHttpInputStream
extends InputStream

An implementation of InputStream which is backed by a series of Netty ByteBuf objects which are gathered from a series of HttpContent messages.

The contents of the InputStream is considered to be the contents of the internal buffers in the order the buffers are inserted into the stream.

The stream must eventually receive a LastHttpContent or the consumer will never receive the EOF signal.

Since:
2.0
Version:
2.0
Author:
